[ c u d e m ]

CUDEM is a set of Python modules and console scripts for utilizing elevation data and Digital Elevation Models.

==============================================
Requires:
==============================================

Python >= 3
GDAL

======================
Optional:
======================

GMT
MB-System
VDatum >= 4
laszip

==============================================
Provides:
==============================================

======================
Console Scripts:
======================
dlim - process data and datalists
regions - process regions
waffles - generate a Digital Elevation Model
fetches - fetch elevation data
spatial_metadata - generate spatial metadata
uncertainties - calculate DEM uncertainties

======================
Scripts:
======================
gdal_null.py
gdal_outliers.py
gdal_nan2null.py
gdal_findreplace.py
gdal_query.py
gdal_chunk.py
gdal_crop.py
gdal_cut.py
gdal_clip.py
gdal_split.py
gdal_percentile.py
gdal_histogram.py
gdal_hillshade.py
gdal_minmax.py
ddms.py
has_nulls.py
xyz_clip.py
clip_xyz.sh
percentiles_minmax.py
outliers_shp.sh
usace_interp.sh
spatial-meta.sh
hillshade.sh
colortable.py
coastline2xyz.sh
create_datalist.sh
create_outliers.sh
create_povray_template.sh
tif2chunks2xyz.sh
bag2tif2chunks2xyz.sh

==============================================
Installation:
==============================================

======================
via git and pip:
======================

 % git clone https:/github.com/ciresdem/cudem.git
 % cd cudem
 % pip install --user --upgrade ./

======================
via git and setup.py:
======================

 % git clone https://github.com/ciresdem/cudem.git
 % cd cudem
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

======================
via zip and setup.py:
======================

 % wget https://github.com/ciresdem/cudem/archive/master.zip
 % unzip master.zip
 % cd master
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

======================
Uninstall from setup.py:
======================
 
 % sudo python setup.py clean
 % sudo xargs rm -r < cudem.install

======================
Update with setup.py:
======================

 % git pull
 % sudo python setup.py clean
 % sudo xargs rm -r < cudem.install
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

